title: Description heading of the retailer
description: Since 2013 millions of users have ordered food online with us helping us grow and to become better to the point of offering food online from thousands of restaurants across India.
terms_and_conditions: Is the restaurant on your way to work or just down the street and you don't mind a walk? You can place an order online with us and pick it up from the restaurant. Many restaurants listed with us have takeaway feature, so you can grab your favorite meal on a go.
how_to_get_this_offer: Should you have any concerns or would you want to give us feedback please do not hesitate to contact our customer service team by using our Live Chat feature on your foodpanda App or website or by sending an email at customercare@foodpanda.in. foodpanda India
